Iii have a question. A musical question.
Do you think music that captures the idea of lovecraftian is possible? I don't mean the racism idea, I mean the unthinkable, the ununderstandable, the wrong but still right.
I know that music is the expression of patterns humans inherently understand but can it... not? Is that even possible?
I'm sorry if I'm fundamentally misunderstanding music here, I'm just a lowly writer but I really want to know if my Ideas work before I print them.
